OL,3,CFestival-goers urged not to bring
OL,4,Cwheelie bins of alcohol on trains
OL,6,FEast Midlands Railway are asking
OL,7,Fpeople travelling to Download Festival
OL,8,Fto plan ahead of their journey to the
OL,9,Ffestival next month.
OL,11,FThey are being reminded not to board
OL,12,Fwith wheelie bins full of alcohol or
OL,13,Fluggage trolleys and to only pack what
OL,14,Fthey can comfortably carry, as luggage
OL,15,Ftrolleys are not permitted on train
OL,16,Fservices.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
