CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1779307554
OL,3,CFestival-goers urged not to bring
OL,4,Cwheelie bins of alcohol on trains
OL,6,FDownload Festival, which takes part in
OL,7,FDonington Park in Leicestershire, is
OL,8,Fthe second largest festival in the UK
OL,9,Fand attracts more than 110,000 fans
OL,10,Feach year.
OL,12,FThe festival will take place on the 10-
OL,13,F14 of June and will feature headliners
OL,14,FLimpbizkit, Guns N'Roses and Linkin
OL,15,FPark.
OL,17,FThe railway operator say some
OL,18,Fcustomers attempted to travel with
OL,19,Fwheelie bins last year filled with
OL,20,Fbeer cans and bottles.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1779307554
OL,3,CFestival-goers urged not to bring
OL,4,Cwheelie bins of alcohol on trains
OL,6,FEngineering work will also affect
OL,7,Fservices on routes to and from London
OL,8,FSt Pancras over the weekend.
OL,10,FIt will mean that some lines will be
OL,11,Fclosed on Saturday and Sunday,
OL,12,Fresulting in a reduced timetable and
OL,13,Fsome replacement bus services.
OL,15,FPeople are being advised to check the
OL,16,FEast Midlands Railway website for more
OL,17,Finformation.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
