PN,37304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1779307554
OL,3,CFestival-goers urged not to bring
OL,4,Cwheelie bins of alcohol on trains
OL,6,FA connecting rail replacement bus will
OL,7,Foperate between Kettering and
OL,8,FLeicester, calling at Market
OL,9,FHarborough.
OL,11,FThere will also be a number of other
OL,12,Falterations to services, with some
OL,13,Ftrains running at different times or
OL,14,Fhaving different stopping patterns.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
