OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1779307554
OL,3,CFestival-goers urged not to bring
OL,4,Cwheelie bins of alcohol on trains
OL,6,FPhilippa Cresswell, Customer
OL,7,FExperience Director at East Midlands
OL,8,FRailway, said: "We're advising
OL,9,Fcustomers travelling to Download
OL,10,FFestival to plan their journeys in
OL,11,Fadvance and be aware that essential
OL,12,Fengineering work will affect services
OL,13,Facross the weekend. As a result, some
OL,14,Fservices will be reduced or amended,
OL,15,Fand passengers should check before
OL,16,Fthey travel and allow extra time.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1779307554
OL,3,CFestival-goers urged not to bring
OL,4,Cwheelie bins of alcohol on trains
OL,6,F"We're also encouraging customers to
OL,7,Ftravel light. Last year, some festive
OL,8,Fgoers tried to board services with
OL,9,Fwheelie bins or festival trolleys full
OL,10,Fof beer. While it might seem like a
OL,11,Fgreat idea for getting your supplies
OL,12,Fto the festival, it just isn't safe or
OL,13,Fpossible to bring them onboard train
OL,14,Fservices.
OL,16,F"Our teams will be on hand at stations
OL,17,Fto support customers and help them
OL,18,Fcomplete their journeys, without their
OL,19,Fbins or trolleys, as smoothly as
OL,20,Fpossible."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
